Easier labelling of bars in bar plot
------------------------------------

The new ``labels`` argument of `~matplotlib.axes.Axes.bar` can now 
be used to label each of the bars.

.. code-block:: python

    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

    x = ["a", "b", "c"]
    y = [10, 20, 15]

    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    _ = ax.barh(x, y, labels=x)
    ax.legend()
